  "keyFeatures": [
    "Agent-native API with owl_agent_ keys for fully programmatic observability",
    "CLI with --format json for machine consumption and --format table for humans",
    "Bundled AI skill files that teach coding agents (Claude Code, Codex, etc.) to set up and use OwlMetry",
    "Batch event ingest with deduplication and gzip compression",
    "Structured metrics with startOperation/complete/fail lifecycle tracking and aggregation queries",
    "Funnel analytics with drop-off rates and experiment-aware grouping",
    "Lightweight A/B experiments with client-side variant persistence",
    "Anonymous identity with owl_anon_ IDs and retroactive user claim",
    "Single Postgres deployment — no Kafka, ClickHouse, or Redis required",
    "Monthly-partitioned events table with auto-pruning by database size",
    "Role-based access control: owner > admin > member",
    "Audit trail for all resource mutations, queryable via API and CLI",
    "Swift SDK for iOS, iPadOS, and macOS with background flush support",
    "Zero-dependency Node.js server SDK with serverless wrapHandler support"
  ],
